extendedInfo.description: Time your contactions and keep all data to determine when to go to the hospital.  Remove data if needed and Easily email or text your results to your Doctor.

reviews.title: Could be better
reviews.comment: Im using different contraction applications and find this needs to fix some bugs, the timer is 19:00:00, after exiting the frequency record clears.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great app
